headline: Is It Too Late to Consider Eversource Energy After Its 2025 Share Price Rebound?
summary: Wondering if Eversource Energy at about $67 a share is still good value after its recent rebound, or if you have already missed the easy money? This breakdown will help you cut through the noise. The stock is up 17.1% year to date and 22.9% over the past year, even though it has only nudged 2.3% higher over the last month and is roughly flat over the past week. This hints that sentiment has shifted meaningfully from where it was a few years ago, despite 3 and 5 year returns still being...
